  shareFile(%opt)
    Share file for download. Return download link if success, die in
    otherwise

        %opt: 
            -file_id            => Id of file on google disk

DEPENDENCE
    Net::Google::OAuth, LWP::UserAgent, JSON::XS, URI, HTTP::Request,
    File::Basename

